quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,I do swear by the Day of Judgment
  75,2,And I do swear by the self-reproaching soul
  75,3,Do people think We cannot reassemble their bones
  75,4,Yes ňĻindeedňļ! We are ňĻmostňļ capable of restoring ňĻevenňļ their very fingertips
  75,5,Still people want to deny what is yet to come
  75,6,"asking ňĻmockinglyňļ, ‚ÄúWhen is this Day of Judgment?‚ÄĚ"
  75,7,But when the sight is stunned
  75,8,and the moon is dimmed
  75,9,and the sun and the moon are brought together
  75,10,"on that Day one will cry, ‚ÄúWhere is the escape?‚ÄĚ"
  75,11,But no! There will be no refuge
  75,12,On that Day all will end up before your Lord
  75,13,All will then be informed of what they have sent forth and left behind
  75,14,"In fact, people will testify against their own souls"
  75,15,despite the excuses they come up with
  75,16,Do not rush your tongue trying to memorize ňĻa revelation ofňļ the Quran
  75,17,It is certainly upon Us to ňĻmake youňļ memorize and recite it
  75,18,"So once We have recited a revelation ňĻthrough Gabrielňļ, follow its recitation ňĻcloselyňļ"
  75,19,Then it is surely upon Us to make it clear ňĻto youňļ
  75,20,"But no! In fact, you love this fleeting world"
  75,21,and neglect the Hereafter
  75,22,On that Day ňĻsomeňļ faces will be bright
  75,23,looking at their Lord
  75,24,And ňĻotherňļ faces will be gloomy
  75,25,anticipating something devastating to befall them
  75,26,But no! ňĻBeware of the dayňļ when the soul reaches the collar bone ňĻas it leavesňļ
  75,27,"and it will be said, ‚ÄúIs there any healer ňĻwho can save this lifeňļ?‚ÄĚ"
  75,28,And the dying person realizes it is ňĻtheirňļ time to depart
  75,29,and ňĻthenňļ their feet are tied together ňĻin a shroudňļ
  75,30,On that day they will be driven to your Lord ňĻaloneňļ
  75,31,This denier neither believed nor prayed
  75,32,but persisted in denial and turned away
  75,33,"then went to their own people, walking boastfully"
  75,34,"Woe to you, and more woe"
  75,35,"Again, woe to you, and even more woe"
  75,36,Do people think they will be left without purpose
  75,37,Were they not ňĻonceňļ a sperm-drop emitted
  75,38,"Then they became a clinging clot ňĻof bloodňļ,¬†then He developed and perfected their form"
  75,39,"producing from it both sexes, male and female"
  75,40,Is such ňĻa Creatorňļ unable to bring the dead back to life